<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="HISTORY"><a class="permalink" href="#HISTORY">HISTORY</a></h1>
The original <code class="Nm">sdpd</code> daemon first appeared in
  <span class="Ux">FreeBSD 5.3</span> and was imported into
  <span class="Ux">NetBSD 4.0</span> by <span class="An">Iain Hibbert</span>
  under the sponsorship of <span class="An">Itronix, Inc.</span> This version
  was rewritten by <span class="An">Iain Hibbert</span> for
  <span class="Ux">NetBSD 6.0</span> in order to allow Bluetooth applications to
  fully specify service records.
</section>
